descriptionHtml:
Because Blender is a nothing but a giant headache, I\'m releasing this to the modding community in the hope you can get it working- the skull needs to be rigged to the rabbit skeleton, but I\'ve got no idea how to do that. :)

-------------------------

That\'s right, Jackalopes are finally (well, nearly) in Skyrim!

What\'s a Jackalope, I hear you ask? Why, it\'s a creature from American folklore that\'s said to have the antlers of a deer and the body of a rabbit.

But what are they doing in Skyrim? Maybe they\'re taxidermied zombies made by bored Necromancers, or maybe it\'s a lesser-known servant of the Daedric Prince Hircine! You be the judge!

-----------------------
Install instructions: place the file in Data\\meshes\\actors\\ambient\\hare\\character assets.
author: Jara aka danburite2
